{
  "stem": "15694.6",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now after the last incident where I, well, was nearly shot-- nearly killed-- I said to my father, now we will not survive in this camp.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Goeth will not have anybody survive whether they win or lose the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We have to escape.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as I will show-- at the end, I will show this sketch map.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But there is a part of the parameter of the-- of the camp was where us-- and mostly it's in a fence and another fence that's about a few doors, three meters, away.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then at one stretch of 30, 40 yards, the-- it will-- it run in one-- into one only.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we decided that's where we're going to escape.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we started to plan, to observe, and even a mock game develops among-- between my father and somebody else.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I get it that I wasn't a better pupil at school to know my geography.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But Switzerland was discussed, and in both cases, we would have to go either via Germany or via Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And this-- but all the other places were taken by the Germans, occupied by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So while they played a game of geography, although my father didn't say it's the reason for escape, but, you know, how to plan a route, and I kept quiet because I couldn't say much.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But gen-- gradually, sort of we made a date.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We would-- it would be Saturday night that we would escape.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It would be a night shift at that Saturday.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And it was Thursday or Friday before we went to work-- I came a bit later-- that I looked at the place where we're going to escape.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It's not very far from the metal workshop, the fence.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
